our No Take zone around this
buffer.

620334d0-d718-4eb8-bd59-efac215ecd37-0
00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.937
So what we want to do is we want
to remove this intersection from

620334d0-d718-4eb8-bd59-efac215ecd37-1
00:00:25.937 --> 00:00:28.040
our proposed No Take zone.

e8ca8dc5-e225-46a9-9abb-65cc9ba72a3d-0
