And so this is going to be the
layer that we're applying the

0f49276c-d130-4fab-b71f-6e90674a35be-1
00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.440
erase tool to.

de22231d-1a6b-4180-80c8-e5310d8b5c19-0
