So we'll make sure that we're in
our Geodatabase and we can name

cfe5721f-4624-4870-a524-668e863dc309-1
00:01:27.305 --> 00:01:34.040
it something like spawning
months erased, click save.

b4921173-8673-48fe-8afe-8683af9a7d48-0
